"type":"text","text":"If you call this function from the body of an asynchronous function,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the unsafe task handle passed to the closure is always non-"},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"because an asynchronous function always runs in the context of a task."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if you call this function from the body of a synchronous function,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and that function isn’t executing in the context of any task,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the unsafe task handle is "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Storing an unsafe reference to a task doesn’t affect the task’s actual life cycle,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and the behavior of accessing an unsafe task reference"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"outside of the "},{"code":"withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" method’s closure is unsafe and undefined behavior."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"There’s no safe way to retrieve a reference to the current task"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and save it for long-term use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"To query the current task without saving a reference to it,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use properties like "},{"code":"currentPriority","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you need to store a reference to a task,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create an unstructured task using "},{"code":"Task.detached(priority:operation:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["/documentation/swift/withunsafecurrenttask(body:)-6gvhl"]}],"metadata":{"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Function","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"withUnsafeCurrentTask"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"T"},{"kind":"text","text":">("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"body"},{"kind":"text","text":": ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sct","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeCurrentTask"},{"kind":"text","text":"?) "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"throws"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency21withUnsafeCurrentTask4bodyxxSctSgKXE_tKlF1TL_xmfp","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"T"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"rethrows"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:12_Concurrency21withUnsafeCurrentTask4bodyxxSctSgKXE_tKlF1TL_xmfp","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"T"}],"externalID":"s:12_Concurrency21withUnsafeCurrentTask4bodyxxSctSgKXE_tKlF","title":"withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)","modules":[{"name":"Swift","relatedModules":[]}],"symbolKind":"func"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)-6gvhl","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Calls a closure with an unsafe reference to the current task."}],"references":{"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)-6gvhl":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)-6gvhl","type":"topic","title":"withUnsafeCurrentTask(body:)","kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift/withunsafecurrenttask(body:)-6gvhl","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withUnsafeCurrentTask","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text